name: O-Bling! Home Button Stickers compatible with iPhone/iPad/iPod touch with the Obama logo!
description:
One pack of Home Button Stickers compatible with Apple, iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, made with the Obama logo!

If your Apple, iPhone, iPad, iPod touch HOME button needs a makeover it may be time to jazz it up with this Obama Campaign Logo home button sticker.

Or, be creative...stick these awesome little stickers on anything you like...t-shirts, purses, dresses, shoes, books, foreheads...you name it!

No tools required; just peel and stick.
 
Includes: 6 home button stickers (one for every Apple device you own!)

name: Peace Car Flag
description: This is car flag is double sided with extra strong nylon fabric...not like those cheap-o car flags. And the pole is extra-strong. We need sturdy cause we have to fly this flag for a long time. Peace is hard. While not related to the election, Peace is good anytime. Approx. 15" x 11".
